INSERT INTO station_transitions (id, workflow_id, source_station_id, target_station_id, condition, label, condition_type, condition_expression)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)
               RETURNING
                id as "id!: Uuid",
                workflow_id as "workflow_id!: Uuid",
                source_station_id as "source_station_id!: Uuid",
                target_station_id as "target_station_id!: Uuid",
                condition,
                label,
                condition_type,
                condition_expression,
                created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
